出領導才能。"},{"pid":"59255ce7424f85b6955ff7bf33523c62334d3375","tid":410083,"uid":23878,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"袁志偉一定要殺"},{"pid":"7d19d68d553bbcd2065e1fb480de05d548f40681","tid":410083,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前仲cut到肥彭淨係話唔應該奚落死者家人同唔支持港獨添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/59c0ddc8e60383a452869221/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F59c0ddc8e60383a452869221%2F&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=31fd45d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/59c0ddc8e60383a452869221/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>彭定康指言論自由有限制 奚落死者家人明顯不正確</strong><br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康認為，言論自由亦有限制，奚落死者家人顯然是不正確，又認為提倡「港獨」只會削弱社會對民主的支持。<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康指：「我認為維護言論自由是非常重要，但亦有一定的限制，尤其考慮是否合乎禮節，舉例說為某人的自殺，或諾貝爾得獎人的死亡表示欣喜，我不認為是正確的。我認為各方都應該冷靜下來，你們都知道我對『港獨』的看法，我上次來港的時候說過，這概念是非常差和不可能，我認為會削弱社會對民主的支持。」<br />\n<br />\n正在訪港的彭定康表示，有信心大學校長能處理好校園出現「港獨」標語的事件，又認為香港仍是亞洲最自由城市之一，並相信行政長官林鄭月娥能夠展示出領導才能。</blockquote><br />\n唔敢提肥彭插強國猿同林鄭，再睇cable訪問完全兩回事"},{"pid":"d93c9f51f6111eb96413e433607438c9fb596645","tid":410083,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"如果now再多個台24小時播新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c18ccf92c511147528a372a5a9cc765c25dd219","tid":410083,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">newlife五毛起底</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bzoe9k7q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbzoe9k7q&h=99ae6483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fgzy3w50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffgzy3w50&h=b